# Maintainer playbook (local only)

Copy this file to **`MAINTAINER.md`** in the bundle root. **`MAINTAINER.md` is gitignored** — do not commit org names, internal repo slugs, or machine-specific paths.

**Full maintainer playbook** (local Cursor bootstrap, adopt loop, verify, release checklists) lives in **`MAINTAINER.md` only**. Copy from a teammate’s `MAINTAINER.md` or ask a bundle maintainer for the standard sections.

## Local setup (fill in after copy)

| Field | Your value |
|-------|------------|
| `WORKFLOWS_BUNDLE_PATH` | e.g. `~/Repos/lsi/current/cursor-dev-workflows` |
| Adopter repos | e.g. `video-encoder`, `web` |
| Layout | **LSI only** — `.lsi/workflows/` (see [docs/adoption-layout.md](docs/adoption-layout.md)) |

## Sections to add in gitignored MAINTAINER.md

- Local Cursor install (`bootstrap-maintainer-local.sh`, `/lsi:update --local-only`)
- Adopt / re-sync loop (`adopt.py`, `update-workflows.py`, `/lsi:update`)
- Verify all adopters
- Register new adopter
- Pre-release and release checklists

Public adopter docs: [docs/adopt-and-update.md](docs/adopt-and-update.md). Patch registry: [patches/README.md](patches/README.md).
